TopicTitle: CRS-15 Livestream hosted by me and a bunch of other people

Articles.Content:
Me(@everydayrocketry on instagram) and along with a bunch of other big instagram space accounts are teaming up to host a livestream for CRS-15 on youtube! We will start at around t-30 min and hopefully see quite some of you guys roll up! See you there!
